<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.1.5">
<l>muppō tumkaṭain tīṇṭiya veṇṇeyi ṉōṭu tayirum viḻuṅki</l>
<l>kappā lāyarkaḷ kāviṟ koṇarnta kalattoṭu cāyttup paruki</l>
<l>meyppā luṇṭaḻu piḷḷaikaḷ pōlanī vimmivim miyaḻu kiṉṟa</l>
<l>appā vuṉṉai yaṟintukoṇ ṭēṉuṉak kañcuva ṉammam taravē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lord who, devouring the curds and butter</l>
<l rend="indent">that [I had] gathered, having churning [it] three times,</l>
<l>And tipping and drinking the pots that had been brought,</l>
<l rend="indent">carried by herders on a pole,</l>
<l>is sobing and sobing,</l>
<l rend="indent">wailing like crying children drinking breast milk!</l>
<l>I have come to know you,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] I am afraid to give you [my] breast milk.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
